---

This software implements the methodology described in:

Carrion-i-Silvestre, J.L. and Gadea, M.D. (2013). "GLS-based unit root tests
for bounded processes." Economics Letters, 120(2), 184-187.
https://doi.org/10.1016/j.econlet.2013.04.016

Users of this software should cite the original paper when using it in
academic research.
